The adapter seems to be a [http://web.archive.org/web/20060110031735/http://www.goodway.com.tw/en/prodimg/bpic/ue120_500.jpg '''Good Way''' UE120]. :'''Good Way''''s [http://web.archive.org/web/20060307003851/http://www.goodway.com.tw/japan/prodimg/driver/ue120_1.0.zip drivers for the device], however, indicate the 07a6:0986 USB ID (default AN986 ID) was used..
